      "acceptanceCriteria": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical) with documented V&V and ISO 9001-certified development process. Gradation 2 requires documented solver verification and institutional QA procedures.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2023 R1 used under institutional license. Solver-level verification documentation and release notes reviewed. FDA FEA team operates under a documented quality management system. Achieved level meets required level."
